                    input(type='text' id='churchPhone' name='churchPhone')

            section
                h3 B. Educational Background 教育背景
                div.section-desc
                    div Original Post-Secondary School(s) Transcripts are to be sent to the Admissions Office, directly from each institution attended after high school, even though a full term may not have been completed and no credits earned. All original transcripts received will be retained for record. 
                    div 高中以上學歷謄本（無論是否完成整個課程），均需由學校直接寄至註冊處，成績單將不予退還。
                
                table(style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 2rem;")
                    tr
                        th(style="width: 30%; text-align:left; font-weight:normal; vertical-align:bottom")
                            div Name of Institution (must include the name in English)
                            div.required 學院名稱 
                        th(style="width: 20%; text-align:left; font-weight:normal; vertical-align:bottom")
                            div Country 
                            div.required 國家
                        th(style="text-align:left; font-weight:normal; vertical-align:bottom")
                            div Period of Attendance 
                            div.required 入讀時間
                        th(style="width: 30%; text-align:left; font-weight:normal; vertical-align:bottom")
                            div Certificate/Diploma/Degree Earned (Specify if applicable)
                            div.required 獲取學位/文憑
                    tr(style="vertical-align:text-top")
                        td.question.required                            
                            input(type='text' id='institutionName1' name='institutionName1' style='width:100%;')                
                        td.question.required
                            input(type='text' id='institutionCountry1' name='institutionCountry1' style='width:100%;')
                        td.question.required
                            input(type='text' id='institutionAttendancePeriod1' name='institutionAttendancePeriod1' style='width:100%;')
                        td.question.required
                            input(type='text' id='institutionEarned1' name='institutionEarned1' style='width:100%;')
                    tr
                        td(style="padding-bottom: 1rem;")
                            input(type='text' id='institutionName2' name='institutionName2' style='width:100%;')                
                        td(style="padding-bottom: 1rem;")
                            input(type='text' id='institutionCountry2' name='institutionCountry2' style='width:100%;')
                        td(style="padding-bottom: 1rem;")
                            input(type='text' id='institutionAttendancePeriod2' name='institutionAttendancePeriod2' style='width:100%;')
