                            input(type='text' id='institutionEarned5' name='institutionEarned5' style='width:100%;')                            

                div
                    div Please prepare official transcripts sent to CCST Vancouver
                    div 請向你曾修讀大專或以上課程的學校,將成績單正本寄到 "加神溫哥華" 


                div.question.required
                    label(for='transferCredit') 
                        span Will you be applying for transfer credit from other institution(s)? 
                        br
                        span 你會否申請把其他學院的學分轉至本校？
                    select(name='transferCredit' id='transferCredit')
                        option(value='') Choose
                        option(value='yes') Yes
                        option(value='no') No

                h3 Application to other Seminary or University 其他學院之申請
                div.question.required
                    label(for='otherApplication') 
                        span Have you applied or studied a similar program in other Seminary or University in the last 10 years? 
                        br
                        span 你曾否於過去十年申請或就讀其他院校之神學/宗教教育或同類課程？
                    select(name='otherApplication' id='otherApplication')
                        option(value='') Choose
                        option(value='yes') Yes
                        option(value='no') No
                div.question
                    label(for='englishRequirement') 
                        span English Language Requirement 
                        br
                        span 英語成績                    
                    div
                        input(type='radio' id='ielts' name='englishRequirement' value='IELTS')
                        label(for='ielts') IELTS Academic 雅思 (學術類)
                    div
                        input(type='radio' id='toefl_IBT' name='englishRequirement' value='TOEFL (IBT)')
                        label(for='toefl_IBT') TOEFL 托福 (IBT) - (加神溫哥華 DI Code C781)
                    div
                        input(type='radio' id='toefl_ITP' name='englishRequirement' value='TOEFL (ITP)')
                        label(for='toefl_ITP') TOEFL 托福 (ITP)                        
                div.question
                    label(for='englishRequirementDateTaken') 
                        span Date Taken 
                        br
                        span 考試日期
                    input(type='date' id='englishRequirementDateTaken' name='englishRequirementDateTaken')
                div.question
                    label(for='englishRequirementScore') 
                        span Score 
                        br
                        span 成績
                    input(type='text' id='englishRequirementScore' name='englishRequirementScore')
                div.section-desc
                    div A minimum score of 30 for TOEFL IBT, 399 for TOEFL ITP, or 4.0 for IELTS (Academic) is required for master programs' applicants who have NOT studied full time for 3 years in a postsecondary institution, where English is the language of instruction and examination, in an English speaking country. Only test scores dating no more than two years are valid.
                    div 若碩士課程申請者沒有在位於以英語為主要語言的國家, 並以英語為教學及考試語言的專上學院全時間地就讀過三年，對其英語考試最低成績要求為托福 IBT 30分, 托福 ITP 399分, 或雅思(學術類) 4.0. 只有兩年內的考試成績才有效。 
                    div A minimum score of 32 for TOEFL IBT, 430 for TOEFL ITP, or 4.5 for IELTS (Academic) is required for doctoral program's applicants who have NOT studied full time for 3 years in a postsecondary institution, where English is the language of instruction and examination, in an English speaking country. Only test scores dating no more than two years when your application is reviewed are accepted.                    
                    div 若博士課程申請者沒有在位於以英語為主要語言的國家, 並以英語為教學及考試語言的專上學院全時間地就讀過三年，對其英語考試最低成績要求為托福 IBT 32分, 托福 ITP 433分, 或雅思(學術類) 4.5。 只有兩年內的考試成績才有效。
                    div Please prepare an official record from IELTS or TOEFL Center and send to CCST Vancouver
                    div 請向雅思或托福機關申請將成績直接送往 "加神溫哥華"

            section
                h3 C. Calling Testimony 蒙召見證
                div.question.required
                    label(for='personalSalvation') 
                        span Please hand in an article regarding your personal salvation and ministry calling. Please upload in PDF format.
                        br
                        span 請書寫一篇得救及蒙召見證。(可用中文書寫, 1000字內)。請以PDF格式上載文件。
                    //- textarea(id='personalSalvation' name='personalSalvation')
                    input(type='file' name='personalSalvation' id='personalSalvation' accept=".pdf" style='padding-bottom:0;')
                    div.error(id='personalSalvationError')
                    input(type='hidden' name='personalSalvationName' id='personalSalvationName')
                    input(type='hidden' name='personalSalvationEncoded' id='personalSalvationEncoded')
                    input(type='hidden' name='personalSalvationType' id='personalSalvationType')
                div.question
                    label(for='spouseSupportLetter') 
                        span If married, please attach a letter of support from your spouse. (M.Div. / M.Min &amp; D. Min. Applicant ONLY.)
                        br
                        span 已婚者需請配偶書寫其對你報名的推薦。 (只適用於道學碩士課程, 教牧學碩士及教牧學博士的申請人)
                    //- textarea(id='spouseSupportLetter' name='spouseSupportLetter') 
                    input(type='file' name='spouseSupportLetter' id='spouseSupportLetter' accept=".pdf" style='padding-bottom:0;')
                    div.error(id='spouseSupportLetterError')
                    input(type='hidden' name='spouseSupportLetterName' id='spouseSupportLetterName')
                    input(type='hidden' name='spouseSupportLetterEncoded' id='spouseSupportLetterEncoded')
                    input(type='hidden' name='spouseSupportLetterType' id='spouseSupportLetterType')                          
            
            section
                h3 D. 研究文章 (只適用於博士課程申請人)         
                div.question
                    label(for='researchPaper') 
                        span Please submit a biblical or theological research paper that you have written. (Please upload in PDF format.)
                        br
                        span 請提交一篇由你所書寫的神學或聖經的研究文章。 (請以PDF格式上載文件。)
                    //- textarea(id='researchPaper' name='researchPaper')  
                    input(type='file' name='researchPaper' id='researchPaper' accept=".pdf" style='padding-bottom:0;')
                    div.error(id='researchPaperError')
                    input(type='hidden' name='researchPaperName' id='researchPaperName')
                    input(type='hidden' name='researchPaperEncoded' id='researchPaperEncoded')
                    input(type='hidden' name='researchPaperType' id='researchPaperType')              

            section
                h3 E. Planned Date of Entry 計劃入學日期
                div.question.required
                    label(for='dateOfEntry') 
                        span Date of Entry 
                        br
                        span 入學日期
                    div
                        input(type='radio' id='fall' name='dateOfEntry' value='fall')
                        label(for='fall') Fall 秋季 (September 九月)
                    div
                        input(type='radio' id='spring' name='dateOfEntry' value='spring')
                        label(for='spring') Spring 春季 (January 一月)
                    div
                        input(type='radio' id='summer' name='dateOfEntry' value='summer')
                        label(for='summer') Summer 夏季 (May 五月)                    
                div.question.required
                    label(for='yearOfEntry') 
                        span Year of Entry 
                        br
                        span 入學年份
                    input(type='text' id='yearOfEntry' name='yearOfEntry')   

            section
                h3  F. Your Referees 推薦人資料
                div.section-desc 
                    div Your Referees (MTS applicant – two reference letters are required; MDiv, MMin and DMin applicant – three reference listed below are requireed.)
                    div 申請人需下載相關推薦信檔案, 邀請推薦人填寫, 並直接郵寄或電郵到本校。
                    ul(style="padding:0; padding-left:30px; padding-top:5px; padding-bottom:15px; margin:0")
                        li 神學研究課程的申請人, 需要兩份推薦。
                        li 道學碩士課程及教牧學碩士課程, 三份不同類別的推薦包括: 所屬教會牧者 + 教牧推薦 + 學術或雇主。
                        li 教牧學博士課程, 三份不同類別的推薦包括: 所屬教會牧者 + 教會或機構認可信 / 教牧推薦 + 學術。
                    div
                        div(style='padding-bottom:5px;')
                            span(style="text-decoration: underline; font-weight:bold") 教牧學博士課程
                            span 申請人請注意:
                        div 收到你的申請表後, 本校將要求你呈交
                        ul(style="padding:0; padding-left:30px; padding-top:5px; margin:0")
                            li Curriculum Vitae / 事奉履歷表
                            li 
                                div Letter of Endorsement/ 教會或機構認可信 *
                                div (if not applicable, applicant should prepare one extra pastoral reference letter)
                                div (申請人若未能提供教會或機構認可信, 則需遞交多一份教牧推薦)

                div.question.required
                    label(for='referenceHomeChurch') 
                        span Home Church Pastoral Reference 
                        br
                        span 所屬教會牧者推薦
                    textarea.short(id='referenceHomeChurch' name='referenceHomeChurch')   
                    div.helper 
                        div Name (in Chinese & English), Position/Title, Telephone, E-mail, Name of Church, Connection to the Applicant
                        div 
                            span Please download the 
                            a(href='../../pdf/ReferenceHomeChurchEng.pdf' target='_blank') letter for the Home Chruch Pastoral Reference
                        div 
                            span 請在此下載
                            a(href='../../pdf/ReferenceHomeChurch.pdf' target='_blank') 所屬教會牧者推薦 

                div.question.required
                    label(for='referencePastoral') 
                        span Pastoral/Lay Leader Reference 
                        br
                        span 教牧推薦人 
                    textarea.short(id='referencePastoral' name='referencePastoral')   
                    div.helper 
                        div Name (in Chinese & English), Position/Title, Telephone, E-mail, Name of Church, Connection to the Applicant
                        div 
                            span Please download the 
